hopobject.body: Will I get paid for overtime? acheter cialis 5 mg comprim pellicul bote de 28 The small town of Steenvoorde in French Flanders is set among hop fields about halfway between Dunkirk and Lille. It holds its annual hop festival during the first weekend of October when an area is set aside in the pretty, grand place for a selection of local brewers to showcase their wares. Try the tasty Fromulus biere de garde, or an Esquelbecq blonde beer from the next village. Other producers offer pâté or cheese flavoured with hops.
